{"tid":571200,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"吉利成平治母企最大股東","createTime":"2018-02-24T12:23:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-25T08:57:13.000Z","uid":10757,"like":4,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"e739b914a11f55672bf06cec2422240a8903117a","tid":571200,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T12:23:41.000Z","msg":"吉利（0175）董事長李書福斥73億歐元（約702億港元）入股平治（Mercedes-Benz）母企德國車廠戴姆勒（Daimler），成為最大單一股東。<br />\n<br />\n彭博早前報道，吉利增持戴姆勒股份至接近10%，戴姆勒隨後就此作出申報，披露李書福透過投資基金增持相關股份。  <br />\n<br />\n其後吉利證實，是以母公司吉利集團的名義收購。<br />\n<br />\n吉利早前已收購北歐汽車品牌Volvo，入股戴姆勒被視為是入主歐洲高端汽車市場的重要一步。"},{"pid":"5603aff10181366ebc2b69f9ae9e22b9ac9009b6","tid":571200,"uid":52215,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T12:25:14.000Z","msg":"啱啱過年返鄉下揸過親戚部吉利帝豪<br />\n幾好，拍得住camry"},{"pid":"eb2994b197aadbaff2c1c7435f21915f47800dde","tid":571200,"uid":3122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T12:26:11.000Z","msg":"平治<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64ce8f362513caf2b5820a4748b4e49a43d6b633","tid":571200,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"5603aff10181366ebc2b69f9ae9e22b9ac9009b6","tid":571200,"uid":52215,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T12:25:14.000Z","msg":"啱啱過年返鄉下揸過親戚部吉利帝豪<br />\n幾好，拍得住camry"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T12:26:27.000Z","msg":"講錯<br />\n應該係corolla"},{"pid":"6c646c6a033d94afb7165e339eb332c8091e4241","tid":571200,"uid":91060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T13:57:15.000Z","msg":"星期一重入吉利！"},{"pid":"cd19aa4aae76acbd9df14875df790fac68cb1657","tid":571200,"uid":94484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T14:09:30.000Z","msg":"各位蟹緊O既巴打<br />\n有機會返家鄉喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19cbbf718b6916f7d2db078073cad7347588967b","tid":571200,"uid":93633,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime